*Narod* je obično bio radostan kada bi slavio uspešne sportske rezultate. (The people were usually joyous when celebrating successful sports results.)

Kako bi se *narod* obradovao, učestvovali su u mnogim proslavama. (In order to make the people rejoice, they participated in many celebrations.)

Učitelji su se trudili da nauče *narod* najvažnije stvari u životu. (Teachers strived to teach the people the most important things in life.)

Vlada je uvela nove mjere kako bi pomogla *narodu*. (The government implemented new measures to help the people.)

*Narod* je bio podeljen po pitanju donošenja odluke. (The people were divided on the matter of making a decision.)